import { Divider } from "@material-ui/core"
import DataInput from "./DataInput"
import TextInput from "./TextInput"
const MainForm = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Divider />
                <DataInput type="datetime-local" title="Data ir Laikas"/>    
                <TextInput />
            <Divider />
        </>
    )
}

export default MainForm
